      "text": "Kay was created by an Italian immigrant's daughter who fell in love with a greaser boy.\nThere was a knife fight at a diner. Gwyn ap Nudd, the King of Annwn (the Celtic Otherworld),\nintervened. The boy lived, but there was a price.",
