    {
      "text": "That story sits heavy in Kay. It's grief, it's origin, it's the price paid for his existence.\nThe loss of his mother is woven into who he is - not as trauma, exactly, but as foundational\ntruth. He thinks about it sometimes. The binding. The loss. The cost of his being here.",
